paragraphs.text: i'm sick and tired of all this giving up, all i hear is talk, and i've had enough. single minded, overwhelmingly one sided. refusing humanity, does not award morality. hope's not dead so we'll forever scream, until it's deafening.
we are the once, who stay awake, while the world sleeps. because we still believe. we are the ones, who will achieve, what the world dreams. because we still believe.

from here on out, i will live deliberately! i can't sit back, to watch the world die, i must fight back! i'll pay the price, there's more to this, not just me!
